  3) STEP 2 - "Add Your Photos" (was: 1 optional avatar + 3 optional gallery
     slots; now: 3 MANDATORY photos, one at a time, matching the old app
     exactly):
    - _mandatoryPhotoCount = 3 (was the 4-photo-cap model). Each upload is
      face-validated on-device via the SAME ML Kit check used everywhere
      else in the app (NoFaceDetectedException) - the old app's "AI
      verification runs on every upload" copy now appears verbatim as
      footer text, but no separate/new verification service was built; it's
      the existing on-device check, labeled to match the old app's wording.
    - Per-photo progress header ("Photo N/3", "N/3 verified"), a 3-segment
      progress bar SEPARATE from the main 4-step wizard progress bar,
