    - Final button changed from plain "Finish" to gradient "Start Matching
      🚀" (GradientButton, matching the old app's CTA style + copy exactly;
      previously onboarding used a flat Material FilledButton, inconsistent
      with the rest of the app's Phase-1-rebuilt screens).

  6) GLOBAL onboarding chrome changes:
    - Scaffold backgroundColor explicitly set to AppColors.bgLight (pale
      pink wash) on every step - was relying on ThemeData's default before.
    - Removed the AppBar("Complete your profile") entirely - the old app's
      wizard has no app bar at all, just the progress bar floating on the
