  7) 90-DAY DATA POLICY MODAL (shared/widgets/info_modals.dart
     InfoModals.dataPolicy, NEW) - pops up once over the Auth/Login screen
     on every fresh app open (features/auth/auth_screen.dart initState +
     addPostFrameCallback), matching the old app's screenshot exactly: 📌
     "90-Day Data Policy" title, X-close top-right, pale-pink info box with
