     one-time-ever dismiss).

  8) EMAIL VERIFICATION SCREEN (features/auth/email_verified_screen.dart,
     REWRITTEN) - was a static "Email verified!" landing screen; now a real
     6-digit OTP code-entry UI matching the old app's screenshots exactly:
     pink circular mail-icon header, "Verify Your Email" + the sent-to email
     interpolated into the body text, 6 individual digit boxes with
